Class HealthCheckDescriptor

java.lang.Object
it.unimore.iot.health.api.datamanager.model.HealthCheckDescriptor
Direct Known Subclasses:
HealthCheckReadRequest
public class HealthCheckDescriptor extends Object
HealthCheckDescriptor is a classic POJO class that describes the structure of a healthcheck.
